<td class="postcell">
<div>
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="description">

        <p>I keep rereading <a href="http://docs.docker.io/en/latest/terms/container/">the Docker.io documentation</a> to try to understand the difference between Docker.io and a full VM. How does it manage to provide a full filesystem, isolated networking environment etc without being as heavy?</p>

<p>I feel foolish for asking, but why is deploying software to a docker image (if that's the right term) easier than simply deploying to a consistent production environment?</p>

